overview: Bonus DVD released with Origins, the sixth full-length album by Swiss folk metal band Eluveitie. The album was released on 1 August 2014 through Nuclear Blast Records. It was the last album to include Anna Murphy, Ivo Henzi and Merlin Sutter as band members.  Contains: The Call Of The Mountains, King, Interview and three performances Live At Feuertanz Festival 2013: The Uprising	, Uxellodunon, 	Havoc.
title: Eluveitie - Origins
